name: Freelancing 101: Turning your Side Hustle into Cash
seo_title: Freelancing 101: Turning your Side Hustle into Cash
seo_description: This class will empower you to take your skills and monetize them as a freelancer. After this class, you will be able to identify competitors, price your services, and develop skills to network so that you can land that next deal.
